---
---
<section class="hero reveal">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Servicio 100% remoto · Todo Paraguay</p>
        <h1>Tu listing, irresistible.<br/>En 24 horas.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Mandanos las fotos y el texto. Nosotros las mejoramos, decoramos digitalmente y corregimos todo — vos solo publicás.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
            <button class="btn-primary" id="heroCtaBtn" type="button">Mejorar mi publicación</button>
            <span class="hero-modes">Handoff $49 · Completo $89</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        padding: 160px 0 100px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(232, 194, 122, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent-color);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        line-height: 1.1;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-sub {
        color: var(--text-dim);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent-color);
        color: #0f0f0f;
        border: none;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
        font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
        background: #d4ae65;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .hero-modes {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero {
            padding-top: 140px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.15rem;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .hero-sub {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            max-width: 280px;
        }
    }
</style>

<script>
    document.getElementById('heroCtaBtn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
        window.dispatchEvent(new Event('toggle-modal'));
    });
</script>
